{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1681-08_294","head":{"value":"La Chate, métamorphosée en Femme. Fable","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", août 1681 [tome 9], p. 294-298.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Le Gentilhomme qui se cache sous le nom du Berger fidelle des Accates, continuë à me faire part de ses Ouvrages. Vous les aimez, &amp; je ne veux pas diférer à vous donner le plaisir de voir l’agreable tour qu’il donne à la Satyre, que je vous ay quelquefois entendu faire contre ceux, dont les grands biens acquis par bonheur font tout le mérite.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#1":{"value":"LA CHATE, METAMORPHOSÉE EN FEMME.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"FABLE.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#2"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des agrémens de l’esprit,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les foiblesses du cœur tirent leur origine.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous le verrez dans la Fable qui suit.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Certain Grec d’assez bonne mine,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais fol à plus de vingt carats,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avoit sans cesse entre ses bras","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Une Chate d’humeur badine,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et grande mangeuse de Rats.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il l’aimoit de toute son ame,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cela parut assez un jour","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[10]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que dans l’ardeur de son amour","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[10]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il pria Jupiter de la changer en Femme.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[11]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[12]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ses vœux eurent l’heureux succés","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[12]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[13]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que s’estoit proposé sa flâme.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[13]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Chate en un moment fut une belle Dame,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[14]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De vertu peu farouche, &amp; de facile accés.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[15]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne croyez pas pourtant que nostre Maniacle","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[16]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[17]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le fut jusqu’à perdre le temps","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[17]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[18]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À faire au Dieu de longs remercîmens","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[18]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[19]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sur la faveur d’un si rare miracle.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[19]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":"  ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[20]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il sauta d’abord au cou","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[20]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De cette Iris de fabrique nouvelle,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[21]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et sans un maudit Rat qui faisoit sentinelle","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[22]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[23]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À quelques pas de son trou.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[23]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans ce qu’il sentoit pour elle","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[24]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Peut-estre eust-il fait le fou ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[25]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais dés l’instant que la Belle","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[26]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui n’avoit pas apparemment","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[27]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Autant d’ardeur que son Amant,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[28]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Eut apperçeu ce Trouble-feste,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[29]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle fondit sur luy si brusquement,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[30]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il n’eut pas le loisir de songer seulement","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[31]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[32]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À faire une retraite honneste.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[32]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les grands biens &amp; les honneurs","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne sçauroient changer les mœurs.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un Homme que le Sort a tiré de la bouë","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour l’élever au plus haut de sa Rouë,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fait toûjours quelque action","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui découvre à nos yeux sa basse extraction.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}}]}}]}}}